'''B'TWIN'''是法国运动装备零售商[[迪卡侬|迪卡侬]]旗下自行车运动的品牌，在全球千余家迪卡侬门店中进行销售。

==历史==
1976年迪卡侬成立自行车运动部门，1986年推出首款自有品牌的整车。1999年推出的B'TWIN 5获得成功，使B'TWIN在迪卡侬下属品牌中成为盈利最多的品牌之一。<ref>{{cite web |title=A Brief History of B’TWIN |url=https://decathlonuk.wordpress.com/2013/07/10/a-brief-history-of-btwin/ |website=Decathlon UK |accessdate=2021-03-19 |language=en |date=2013-07-10 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417092556/https://decathlonuk.wordpress.com/2013/07/10/a-brief-history-of-btwin/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Décathlon : une innovation par semaine ! |url=https://www.capital.fr/entreprises-marches/decathlon-une-innovation-par-semaine-895278 |website=Capital.fr |accessdate=2021-03-19 |language=fr |date=2013-12-12 |archive-date=2021-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210401120005/https://www.capital.fr/entreprises-marches/decathlon-une-innovation-par-semaine-895278 }}</ref>

B'TWIN自行车的产品线涵盖从公路车、山地车等专业运动，到旅行车、折叠车、童车等休闲健身。除整车外，也提供大部分的自行车组装零配件和骑行运动装备。

2018年起，迪卡侬在公路和山地自行车领域放弃了B'TWIN品牌，转而使用全新的Triban和Van Rysel品牌。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Bonville-Ginn |first1=Tim |title=Decathlon bikes range: guide to Triban and Van Rysel bikes |url=https://www.cyclingweekly.com/group-tests/triban-bikes-van-rysel-bikes-371063 |website=Cycling Weekly |language=en |date=2020-09-20 |access-date=2021-03-19 |archive-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414221229/https://www.cyclingweekly.com/group-tests/triban-bikes-van-rysel-bikes-371063 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Decathlon launches new high-end bike brand, Van Rysel |url=https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/5924/decathlon-launches-new-high-end-bike-brand-van-rysel |website=Cyclist |language=en}}</ref>

